<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Como foi sua semana?</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <style>
    /* Customização fina e minimalista da barra de scroll global */
    ::-webkit-scrollbar {
        width: 4px;
        height: 4px;
    }
    ::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
        background: transparent;
    }
    ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
        background: rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.25); /* Slate translúcido */
        border-radius: 99px;
    }
    ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover {
        background: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.5); /* Indigo com transparência ao focar */
    }
    html, body {
        scrollbar-width: thin;
        scrollbar-color: rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.25) transparent;
    }
</style>
    <style>
        input[type="radio"] { display: none; }
        input[type="radio"]:checked + label {
            transform: scale(1.3);
            filter: grayscale(0%);
        }
        label {
            filter: grayscale(40%);
            transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        label:hover { filter: grayscale(0%); transform: scale(1.15); }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-slate-50 flex flex-col items-center justify-center min-h-screen font-sans antialiased text-slate-800 p-4">

    <div class="flex justify-between items-center w-full mb-6 pb-4 border-b border-slate-100">
        <div class="text-sm text-slate-500 font-medium">
            Olá, <span class="font-bold text-slate-800"><%= userName %></span> 👋
        </div>
        <a href="/logout" class="text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-400 hover:text-rose-500 transition-colors flex items-center gap-1 bg-slate-50 px-2 py-1 rounded-md border border-slate-100">
            Sair <span>→</span>
        </a>
    </div>
    
    <div class="bg-white p-10 rounded-3xl shadow-xl shadow-slate-100/70 max-w-xl w-full border border-slate-100">
        <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 text-center mb-1">Como foi sua semana?</h1>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 text-center mb-10">Sua resposta é confidencial e ajuda a calibrar nossa jornada.</p>

        <form action="/submit-feedback" method="POST" class="space-y-8">
            
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center bg-slate-50/50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100">
                <div class="text-center">
                    <input type="radio" id="sent1" name="sentiment" value="1" required>
                    <label for="sent1" class="text-4xl block pb-1">😫</label>
                </div>
                <div class="text-center">
                    <input type="radio" id="sent2" name="sentiment" value="2">
                    <label for="sent2" class="text-4xl block pb-1">😕</label>
                </div>
                <div class="text-center">
                    <input type="radio" id="sent3" name="sentiment" value="3">
                    <label for="sent3" class="text-4xl block pb-1">😐</label>
                </div>
                <div class="text-center">
                    <input type="radio" id="sent4" name="sentiment" value="4">
                    <label for="sent4" class="text-4xl block pb-1">🙂</label>
                </div>
                <div class="text-center">
                    <input type="radio" id="sent5" name="sentiment" value="5">
                    <label for="sent5" class="text-4xl block pb-1">🤩</label>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="text-left">
                <label class="block text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Marcadores de Contexto (Opcional)</label>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                    <% if (tags && tags.length > 0) { %>
                        <% tags.forEach(tag => { %>
                            <label class="cursor-pointer">
                                <input type="checkbox" name="tags" value="<%= tag.name %>" class="hidden peer">
                                <span class="inline-block bg-white text-slate-600 text-xs px-4 py-2.5 rounded-full font-medium border border-slate-200 peer-checked:bg-indigo-600 peer-checked:text-white peer-checked:border-indigo-600 transition-all duration-150 shadow-sm">
                                    <%= tag.name %>
                                </span>
                            </label>
                        <% }) %>
                    <% } else { %>
                        <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 italic">Nenhum marcador ativo esta semana.</p>
                    <% } %>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="text-left">
                <label class="block text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Comentário Adicional</label>
                <textarea name="comments" rows="3" placeholder="Quer pontuar algo específico que aconteceu?" class="w-full bg-slate-50/50 border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl p-4 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500 outline-none text-sm placeholder-slate-400 resize-none"></textarea>
            </div>

            <button type="submit" class="w-full bg-slate-900 text-white font-semibold py-4 rounded-2xl hover:bg-slate-800 transition shadow-lg shadow-slate-900/10 text-sm">
                Confirmar Envio
            </button>
        </form>
    </div>

</body>
</html>